Package: flat-bridge
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), flatpak
Maintainer: Your Name <you@example.com>
Description: Generate wrapper scripts for Flatpak packages
 flat-bridge is a Bash script that generates a lightweight
 wrapper script to run a Flatpak package via flatpak run.
 It supports custom bridge names, custom binary directories,
 system-wide installs, and bridge removal.
